]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 16:53:19 GMT</pubDate><enclosure url="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg" length="0" type="image/jpeg"/><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>I showed silver gelatin prints, collage, flat work, and film as well as a performance at <a href="https://www.rigaartweek.com/en-events/festival-eden-wet-work-over-lap">Eden: Wet Work Over Lap.</a></strong></p><p>Venue: Kim(?)<br>Location: Riga, Latvia<br>Date: May 29 &#8211; July 11, 2026</p><p>Curator: Zane Onckule<br></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-img" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abe